data.description: METICULOUSLY KEPT HOME by the original owner. Why wait for new constructions? This home has it all! The kitchen features granite countertops, gorgeous backsplash, a gas range, and stainless steel appliances. This home has a ton of storage and fresh interior paint.  Popular open concept opens to a desired back patio featuring MOUNTAIN VIEWS, no rear neighbor, turf, brick pavers, low-maintained landscaping, and a gas grill outlet.
